<section>
	<h2>How to implement</h2>
	<ol>
		<li>Insert a paragraph. The data-inview will be attached to that element.</li>
		<li>Insert a link pointing to the target escaping site.</li>
		<li>Add the <code>wb-exitlink</code> class to the link to enable the exit link feature</li>
	</ol>
	<pre><code>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="wb-exitlink btn btn-success" href="<strong>[The external link like http://www.weather.gc.ca]</strong>" rel="external"&gt;<strong>[Text link]</strong>&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</code></pre>
</section>


<section>
	<h2>Configuration options</h2>
	
	<p>There is no special configuration option.</p>
</section>


